a loaner helm at the time I started.  The armor was carpet, the helm
was a beat-up Spanghelm, but they were enough to give people a 
taste of what they were getting into.  Over the years they were phased
out and I don't know if they were replaced.  
	I'm in the process of getting a loaner helm for our shire here
in Lexington.  I'm ordering a number of helms from an old friend in 
Ansteorra, and charging a $5 extra to cover the cost of the loaner.
