Arval brings up a good point.  Thankyou for thinking about it. 

----------------

Let us look at the initial reason I formed this list.  To spread information
and ideas across geographical boundries.  To provide an information pool.  To
increase communication between SCA participants.  To break down regionalization.

I have not limited the distribution to MEMBERS_ONLY.  Nor, do we limit the
attendance of events to members only.  Another topic for discussion might
be that is my role as a moderator that of a Seneschal, Chronicler, or 
