practice through the last few hundred years.  When a particular
practice is relatively new, it is labeled so.  It does not dwell
overmuch on British heraldry either, but covers practices from
other countries.  There are also a number of examples of modern
heraldry and grants of arms.

The cost is around $20 if I remember correctly (oh, hardback on
